that part above is garbage don't listen to it

listen to this part instead:

shanna-lib is a portable joystick-to-keyboard emulation solution. It fits into
all of your favorite games, essentially allowing you to add text-input
capabilities to any handheld game console. Or others too but I'm focusing on the
handheld consoles for now.



